name: Vergina Kolen
description: I love watching comedies, thrillers&action movies in my apartment-which is my own pretty little sanctuary. Love being active (have even wom a few hula hoop contests), performing live on stage (have done Grease, CATS Hairspray), making home-made gifts, and listening to music of all kinds- especially hip-hop,pop, classic rock and alternative. For a first date, i like surprises, and can have fun games.Exercise your creativity and i’m sure i’ll love it!
